  "title": "Loom in the Java Ecosystem - Inside Java Newscast #34",
  "summary": "Among other things, Java 19 ships with virtual threads, structured concurrency APIs, sealed types, and pattern matching in switch - all of them as previews, but still very cool! I'm using these features here to create a GitHub crawler.",
  "content": "<p>Among other things, Java 19 ships with virtual threads, structured concurrency APIs, sealed types, and pattern matching in <code>switch</code> - all of them as previews, but still very cool! I&#x27;m using these features here to create a GitHub crawler.</p><p>This episode was not scripted and so there&#x27;s no written version of what I said.\nAnother one you gotta watch. 😉</p>\n<p>Here are links to the chapters and all other sources (basically the video description):</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=0m00s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">First Take</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=0m19s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Intro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=1m02s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Project Loom Recap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=4m16s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tooling</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JMC-6679?attachmentViewMode=gallery\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">JDK Mission Control</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://youtrack.jetbrains.com/issue/IDEA-301409/Support-virtual-threads-project-loom\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">IntelliJ</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/microsoft/vscode-java-debug/issues/1159\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">VS Code</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/eclipse-jdt/eclipse.jdt.debug/issues/38\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Eclipse</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/oracle/graal/pull/4802/files\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Graal</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=5m56s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Web Servers</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/eclipse/jetty.project/releases\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Jetty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/netty/netty/issues/8439\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Netty</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tomcat.apache.org/tomcat-10.1-doc/changelog.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Tomcat</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/piranhacloud/piranha/pull/2635\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Piranha Cloud</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=6m33s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Frameworks</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework/issues/23443\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Spring</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/helidon-io/helidon/releases/tag/2.2.0\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Helidon</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://helidon.io/nima\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Helidon Nima</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/micronaut-projects/micronaut-core/issues/7724\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Micronaut</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/pull/24942\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Quarkus</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://mail.openjdk.org/pipermail/loom-dev/2022-July/004844.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Quarkus mail to OpenJDK</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vertx.io/blog/vertx-virtual-threads-incubator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vert.x</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/vert-x3/vertx-virtual-threads-incubator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Vert.x Incubator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://javalin.io/news/javalin-4-development-updates\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Javalin</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM&amp;t=8m15s\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Outro</a></li>\n</ul><p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I9hQvJO39uM\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Watch the video.</a></p>",
